      <title class="- topic/title ">
         <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">252.237-7000</ph> Notice of Special Standards of Responsibility.</title>
      <conbody outputclass="provision" class="- topic/body  concept/conbody ">
         <p class="- topic/p ">As prescribed in <ph xtrc="DFARxref" class="- topic/ph ">
               <xref outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                     class="- topic/xref "
                     base="DFARS-237.270"
                     href="237.270.dita#DFARS-237.270">237.270</xref>
            </ph>(d)(1), use the following provision:</p>
         <p class="- topic/p " outputclass="Ctr_SmCaps">NOTICE OF SPECIAL STANDARDS OF RESPONSIBILITY (DEC 1991)</p>
         <p outputclass="List1" class="- topic/p ">(a)  To be determined responsible, the Offeror must meet the general standards of responsibility set forth at <ph xtrc="FARxref" class="- topic/ph ">FAR 9.104-1</ph> and the following criteria, as described in Chapter 3, General Standards, of “Government Auditing Standards.”</p>
         <p outputclass="List2" class="- topic/p ">(1)  Qualifications;</p>
         <p outputclass="List2" class="- topic/p ">(2)  Independence; and</p>
         <p outputclass="List2" class="- topic/p ">(3)  Quality Control.</p>
         <p outputclass="List1" class="- topic/p ">(b)  “Government Auditing Standards” is issued by the Comptroller General of the United States and is available for sale from the:</p>
         <p class="- topic/p "/>
