         <p outputclass="List1" class="- topic/p "/>
         <p outputclass="List1" class="- topic/p ">(c)  The apparently successful Offeror, before award, shall give the Contracting Officer evidence that it is licensed by the cognizant licensing authority in the state or other political jurisdiction where the Offeror operates its professional practice.</p>
